description: Triangle T(n,k) in which n-th row gives degrees of irreducible representations of alternating group A_n.
references: J. H. Conway, R. T. Curtis, S. P. Norton, R. A. Parker and R. A. Wilson, ATLAS of Finite Groups, Oxford Univ. Press, 1985.
crossrefs: Rows give A003862, A003683, etc. Cf. A060240.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Mar 21 2001
extensions: Characters for A_8 to A_11 from the online MAGMA calculator. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 04 2006
